{"tid":2159862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"拜登慰問弟弟病逝的特朗普　稱了解失去至親巨大痛苦","createTime":"2020-08-16T14:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T17:43:41.000Z","uid":44209,"like":69,"dislike":171,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"4a76b4df40b4e614ceb3d6abe454b7b1f85637f9","tid":2159862,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"拜登慰問弟弟病逝的特朗普　稱了解失去至親巨大痛苦<br />\n<br />\n美國民主黨總統參選人拜登，慰問弟弟病逝的總統特朗普。拜登在社交專頁以「總統先生」稱呼特朗普，並非好像以往的貼文，直呼其名。拜登說知道特朗普弟弟羅伯特離世的消息後，他與太太都感到很難過，又說自己了解失去至親的巨大痛苦，亦知道此時此刻家庭的重要性。羅伯特因病在紐約一間醫院離世，終年71歲。特朗普較早前透過白宮發表聲明，形容羅伯特不單止是他的弟弟，亦是最好的朋友，永遠懷念對方。羅伯特過去為家族地產王國，打理物業投資生意，為人較低調，與做過「真人騷」的哥哥特朗普，風格不同。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-16 22:42:35<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/127569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F127569&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=a03bfc10\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/127569</a>"},{"pid":"a82af31a65e1e61399e02ade48e90b9cc9958e97","tid":2159862,"uid":44209,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"Mr. President, Jill and I are sad to learn of your younger brother Robert&rsquo;s passing. I know the tremendous pain of losing a loved one &mdash; and I know how important family is in moments like these. I hope you know that our prayers are with you all.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joebiden/status/1294978495383310336?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoebiden%2Fstatus%2F1294978495383310336%3Fs%3D21&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=7f485ff1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoebiden%2Fstatus%2F1294978495383310336%3Fs%3D21&h=d39fba16\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joebiden/status/1294978495383310336?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"cb865fca845c3d657b4cba8436de404c557c7b0c","tid":2159862,"uid":286897,"like":63,"dislike":31,"score":32,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":